headline: Keysight and The University of Malaga Open State-of-the-Art 6G Research and Innovation Laboratory
summary: SANTA ROSA, Calif., January 30, 2025--Keysight Technologies, Inc. (NYSE: KEYS) and the University of Malaga (UMA) have opened a 6G research and innovation Lab. The facility is dedicated to advancing 6G technology through comprehensive solutions that address key use cases and technological challenges.
